  "_comment": "Copy to node.json and fill in. node.json is gitignored -- it holds a seat code.",

  "device": "hw:1,0",
  "_device": "ALSA capture device. Run `arecord -l` on the Pi to find it. An I2S HAT is usually hw:1,0; a USB interface is often hw:2,0.",

